name: Hattrick
description: Skull with a top hat on his head, what does he want? Nothing. He just wants to beat up people. "The whole thing ended in frustration. And then the phone rang. It was a woman with a big laugh. "Who are you?" she asked. "A man with a big hat with number 23" I said, and was glad I didn't have to answer. "Well, I'm from Canada, and I don't like those big hats. And I don't like you." "Yeah, you're a crazy man," she said.
